    <summary>Highly portable Acorn Archimedes emulator</summary>
    <description>
    <p>
        ArcEm is a portable open-source emulator for the Acorn Archimedes. It's
        capable of running multiple operating systems including RISC OS and ARM
        Linux.  
    </p>

    <p>
        ArcEm runs on:
        <ul>
            <li>Amiga OS</li>
            <li>Mac OS X</li>
            <li>Microsoft Windows</li>
            <li>RISC OS</li>
            <li>Unix (X Windows)</li>
        </ul>
    </p>
